          "plain_text": "I got my eight hour sleep! Cait must have had about 9 or so. While she was sleeping I walk down a small cafe, do some writing, order two breakfasts and put the scrambled eggs onto the ham and cheese croissant. I watch hordes of Pilgrims walk past down the road outside. ",
          "href": null
