    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "We left a lot later than most other pilgrims today (who got rained on). And didn’t see our Scottish friends unfortunately. That was until near the end of the day when we saw three figures in the distance: Camino girl, Camino mom (or older sister) and the one and only Camino dog. Camino dog was drinking out of a water fountain when we passed, what a legend.  ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "We left a lot later than most other pilgrims today (who got rained on). And didn’t see our Scottish friends unfortunately. That was until near the end of the day when we saw three figures in the distance: Camino girl, Camino mom (or older sister) and the one and only Camino dog. Camino dog was drinking out of a water fountain when we passed, what a legend.  ",
